{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_51_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 莉央と愛へのドッキリ企画",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……どれにしよう……\n困ったなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Which one should I choose…?\nThis is tough…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2233.3333333000005,
          "startTime": 5.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　葵さん、何を書いて……あ、それ『ミラクル\n☆アイドルバースデー！』のアンケートじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Aoi-san‚ what are you writing…? Oh‚ isn't that\nthe \"Miracle ☆ Idol Birthday!\" questionnaire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3999999682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルがしたいことを叶えてくれる、雑誌のお誕生日\n企画ですよね。ついに葵さんの番が来たんですね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's that birthday project in the magazine where they grant\nyour wishes as an idol‚ right? It's finally Aoi-san's turn~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね。でも、何を書こうか悩んでるんだ\nこころに相談して、アイデアは沢山出たんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah. But I'm having trouble deciding what to write.\nI've talked to Kokoro‚ and we've come up with a lot of ideas though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、「莉央にバンジージャンプをしてほしい」とか\n「莉央にぬるぬるの床の上でお相撲をしてほしい」とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ \"I want Rio to bungee jump‚\"\nor \"I want Rio to sumo wrestle on a slippery floor.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで莉央さんに体を張らせようとするんですか！？\nせっかくのお誕生日がギャグになっちゃいますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you trying to make Rio-san do all the physical stuff!?\nYour birthday will turn into a joke!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、莉央のそんな面白……\n体を張った気高い姿が見られるのは今回くらいだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it would be fun… I mean‚\nThis might be the only chance to see her noble figure putting herself on the line.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、撮影当日に向けて練習する莉央と愛の姿を\nこころと二人で密着取材するつもりだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Kokoro and I are planning to do a close-up report on\nRio and Ai practicing for the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "さらっと私までやることになってる！？\n私はともかく、後で絶対莉央さんに怒られますって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ why am I included in this!?\nSetting me aside‚ Rio-san will definitely get angry later!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6916767574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。確かに二人が芸人さん顔負けのことに\n挑戦するのは面白いけど、後が怖いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. It would be funny to see you two take on challenges\nthat rival comedians‚ but the aftermath would be scary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "愛の言う通り、怒りで我を忘れた莉央が\n僕達を消すまで暴れまわるかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like you said‚ Rio might lose her mind with anger\nand rampage until she eliminates us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ。そうなったら命がいくつあっても……\nって、私そんなこと言ってませんよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. If that happens‚ no matter how many lives we have…\nWait‚ I never said anything like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "と、とにかく、他のお願い事にしましょう！\nもっとこう、安全な……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-anyway‚ let's go with another wish!\nSomething more‚ you know‚ safe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　莉央さんの時のが参考になるんじゃない\nですか？　大好きなことをお願い事にする感じの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's it! We can use Rio-san's as a reference‚ right?\nLike‚ making a wish about something you love!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "食べたことないパンケーキを食べたいってお願いだっけ\nまぁ、おかげで編集部の人達が頭を抱えてたけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her wish was to eat pancakes she'd never tried before‚ right?\nWell‚ thanks to that‚ the editorial staff had a headache‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.166666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "都内のパンケーキを食べ歩いてる莉央が\n食べたことないものなんて、探しようがなくてさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Rio's tried pancakes all over the city‚\nthere’s no way to find one she hasn’t had.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、なんとかなったじゃないですか\nなにより、莉央さんが幸せそうにしてましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it worked out‚ didn't it?\nMore importantly‚ Rio-san looked happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんも、大好きなことをお願い事にしちゃいましょう\nその方が当日、何倍も楽しめちゃうはずですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should wish for something you love too‚ Aoi-san.\nThat way‚ you'll enjoy the day many times more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、当日はどうでもいいんだけどなぁ。いや、最初\nから変なお願いをするより、ドッキリとかの方が……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I don't really care about the day itself though. No‚ rather than\nmaking a weird request from the start‚ maybe a prank would be better…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、いや、ありがとう愛。せっかくなら愛の言う通り\n大好きなダンスに関わることにするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no‚ thanks‚ Ai. Since it's a special occasion‚\nI'll follow your advice and make it about dance‚ which I love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A Few Days Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.4333676839
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.4333676839
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 162.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "私達が、葵にダンスを教える……？\nそれってどういう企画なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're going to teach Aoi to dance…?\nWhat kind of project is that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2699.9999999999886,
          "startTime": 165
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 164.6666321753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "編集部からいただいた資料によると、葵さんのお願いは\n今まで踊ったことのないダンスを踊りたい、だそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "According to the materials we received from the editorial department‚\nAoi-san's wish is to try a dance she's never done before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 174.5999655086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんには、当日は様々なダンスに精通したプロが来る\nと伝えておいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're going to tell Aoi-san that professionals versed in various dances\nwould come on the day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6625975999864,
          "startTime": 180.8666625976
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 180.6999614396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "前日までに様々なダンスを覚えた私達が出ていって\n葵をびっくりさせる。その後、教えながら一緒に踊る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ we'll show up after learning various dances beforehand‚\nand surprise Aoi. Then‚ teach her as we dance together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.4666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 191.6666281062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
