      "text": "へ～、サプライズ企画なのね。面白そうじゃない\n書いてあるのも、全部葵が未経験のダンスばかりだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh~‚ a surprise project‚ huh? Sounds fun.\nAll the dances listed here are ones that Aoi has never experienced.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.9999959309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
