      "text": "なら仕方ないわね。誕生日をズラせ、なんて言えないし\n私達だけじゃなくて、スタッフさんの都合もあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then it can't be helped. We can't ask her to postpone her birthday‚\nand the staff have their own schedules too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
